  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the efficacy of a low-volume bowel preparation versus
      a high-volume bowel preparation for bowel cleansing on hospitalized patients undergoing
      colonoscopies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
